snippet.title: Australian Beach Unreal Engine 4 Recreation (free download)
snippet.description:
out now for free on PC with $5 for VR compatibility
itch.io - https://cavesrd.itch.io/australia
steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1400510/Castle_Rock_Beach_West_Australia/

Experience a realistically inspired recreation of Australia's south west coast. Explore the world at your own pace and use the game's photography mechanics to progress with casual objectives. Contains some of the latest visual tech provided by Unreal Engine 4. Hope you guys enjoy this one!

stay updated - https://instagr.am/cavesrd - https://twitter.com/cavesrd
download my exploration games - https://cavesrd.itch.io
do you think real-time graphics could help your project or business? get in touch - mattcvsrd@gmail.com

video soundtrack: "The Map Plotted Us In" by Himalayan Beach Ensemble
